## Development

For developers and contributors:

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/aimasteracc/tree-sitter-analyzer.git
cd tree-sitter-analyzer

# Install development dependencies
uv sync

# Run tests
pytest tests/ -v
```

